"P3561513771" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Crossing the Line</color></span></scale></font><br><br><span align=center><color orange><i>Hero Morality Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You find a copy of what appears to be a kill order put out by a high ranking Longbow official. Reading it you know you can't just sit back and let this happen.<br><br><scale 1.1><font face=computer><color BurlyWood>As many of you know, Maelstrom destroyed one of our secret holding facilities two days ago in an attempt to permanently eliminate the dozen or so prisoners we were holding. While he achieved that goal, he also killed six members of our team. Thereby, I'm official ordering the termination of Maelstrom, also known as Some Cok. We have tracked his location to an old Freakshow hideout. We have no idea what he's doing there, but you can beat he'll be expecting us. Move with caution. </color></font></scale><br><br>There's a picture of Maelstrom and the location of the Freakshow hideout listed on the paper as well."
// Answer Text :
// Page ImHero Text :
// Answer Text :
// Answer Text :
// Page ImVigilante Text :
"P1564689417" "<color orange>WARNING: This is a Morality Mission. Completing this mission will change your current alignment of Vigilante to Hero, removing any progress you may have made on any other alignment. Becoming a Hero again means you will no longer be able to travel to the Rogue Isle. It will sever all times with your villain world.<br><br>Are you sure you want to do this?</color>"
// Page ImRogue Text :
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

